{"tid":2014821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【共匪現身】中国解封後 高速公路＂報復性收費＂村民攔車收過路費","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:32:08.000Z","uid":293677,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2221a88d7a80d8a421d186aefac619d1be42eed2","tid":2014821,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>解封後中國高速公路收費暴漲 民怨斥如土匪攔路搶錢<br />\n</ins></span><br />\n2020-05-13 12:28:04<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國宣稱武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情已經緩解，各地陸續解封，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當局聲稱將帶來一波「報復性消費」，不料報復性消費還未出現，「報復性收費」已經先行，高速公路恢復收費後大漲價，讓許多民眾叫苦連天，甚至有村民攔車收取過路費，土匪行徑讓網友直搖頭。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國在5月6日恢復高速公路收費，許多司機紛紛在網路上秀出自己的收據，顯示高速公路收費飆漲，讓許多卡車司機直喊「車沒法開了！」根據網路上的影片顯示，從四川省巴中市到陝西省城固縣，約210公里的車程，竟要收費人民幣841元（約新台幣3544元）；而1輛空車行經黃河大橋，十幾公里，收費竟高達220元（約新台幣927元）。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，1位貨車司機在網路上貼出兩張收據比較，發現一樣的車型，經過相同的「山東路段臨沂北至龍山線」，去年12月12日收費為55元（約新台幣231元），現在卻要收94元（約新台幣396元），漲幅超過70%，此結果令網友激憤。山東省交通運輸廳官方微博趕緊出來滅火，解釋是法規改變所致，並非趁機漲價。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除了高速公路收費大漲，中國各地也傳出有村民攔截車輛收取過路費的行徑，一個網路影片顯示，有男子推著一位坐輪椅的老婦堵路，隨行的還有一名女子，一夥人霸占道路，硬是向路上車輛討錢，惡霸行徑讓中國有有傻眼，有網友說，這是中國當今社會亂象的縮影，上樑不正下樑歪，共匪的攔路搶劫比這厲害多了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGD6r4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGD6r4S.jpg&h=83b68fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上有共匪，下有土匪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9977db039e82ea591fc0c0a9e0eecd6314527f","tid":2014821,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"幅圖好正"},{"pid":"cd0d96c89f1b1bafef0ba15ba06e76803acbd07f","tid":2014821,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3163859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3163859&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=56f9b297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3163859&h=50181b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3163859</a>"},{"pid":"3b72121cd59a609e05d301425f5914d88afef60f","tid":2014821,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"一部分人聚係富起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ca129b8348493a259ed53459491f7d64c68641","tid":2014821,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一部分人堅係富起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"446393d4fb2cf695289aa0512a3e0f13f5534c2d","tid":2014821,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"this is China<br />\n國情當前, 人民係諗住自肥互害<br />\n咁既國家咁既人民,   你住埋我果份"},{"pid":"fd8258e4d19cade9aed358630021a5ea354825e3","tid":2014821,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446393d4fb2cf695289aa0512a3e0f13f5534c2d","tid":2014821,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"this is China<br />\n國情當前, 人民係諗住自肥互害<br />\n咁既國家咁既人民,   你住埋我果份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"原子費拉"},{"pid":"c7d34036e6a8cbd9a8a33368097f49bc4d532ea9","tid":2014821,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"回鄉創業（土匪）"},{"pid":"b97776f4939ebeac6fdb5eac56ef573b0bab5f66","tid":2014821,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"咱們有膠鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怕"},{"pid":"1e5e74d