 />\n<br />\n咁L樣都叫滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea49c63d429525aff6a906cb411c2cc8ed07cd05","tid":2014821,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"地板油剷過去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451fdfecddfb914de3eeb525e9a80b0c582e41ad","tid":2014821,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"放路釘未"},{"pid":"d11758bc29c41bf0cf96fb8aee118679ab578f4b","tid":2014821,"uid":326725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"呢套邏輯佢哋唔係最鍾意嘅咩<br />\n話咩香港人咪中意中共就唔好喺香港住 唔滿意咪移民囉<br />\n但明明香港係屬於香港人嘅<br />\n即係人地嫌自己間屋風景唔好 街外人就走嚟話你唔鍾意唔好住啦<br />\n<br />\n班韭菜唔滿意個價錢咪唔好用條路囉<br />\n更何況而家條路又唔係屬於佢哋嘅<br />\n學佢哋話齋 咁唔滿意嘅咪自己整條新路出嚟囉"},{"pid":"4aa9f212f9c90194dbc4acaba6b1808ac9814690","tid":2014821,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"如果多公路攔截，搶錢<br />\n代表失業問題真係開始嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國入wto前<br />\n一堆人做賊  <br />\n好多更係成條村的匪村<br />\n<br />\n十幾年變得安全<br />\n一係wto堆外資廠  吸納左好多年輕生產力<br />\n好多匪村 轉型山寨村"},{"pid":"b0e3192bf282ef2d9bee3123f46c3781480c2324","tid":2014821,"uid":100882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446393d4fb2cf695289aa0512a3e0f13f5534c2d","tid":2014821,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"this is China<br />\n國情當前, 人民係諗住自肥互害<br />\n咁既國家咁既人民,   你住埋我果份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"他們很愛國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d73ae2487c18c0bf43af47fd5dea7f4df9e9355","tid":2014821,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"先讓一部份人富起來<br />\n然後<br />\n讓那部份人更富起來<br />\n<img src=\"/a